    From the manufacturer


    Windows 11 brings you closer to what you love

    Family, friends, obsessions, music, creationsWindows 11 is the one place for it all. With a fresh new feel and tools that make it easier to be efficient, it has what you need for whatevers next.

    The New Inpsiron 16 2-in-1

    See your beautiful world whenever you want with the Inspiron 16 2-in-1. Features 16.0-inch display and 16:10 aspect ratio.

    • 16.0" FHD+ WVA AG Touch 60 Hz LBL 300 nits with ComfortView Plus Display, include Active Pen.
    • 12th Generation Intel Core i5-1235U Processors
    • Integrated graphics
    • 512GB Solid State Drive Storage
    • 8GB, 2x4GB, DDR4, 3200MHz Memory

    Read more

    Look and sound your best

    Be seen in high-resolution with a FHD webcam, while wide dynamic range software improves back-lighting and temporal noise reduction hardware decreases pixelation even in low-light environments.

    Make sure youre heard with built-in dual microphones and AI that reduces background noise.

    Need to disconnect? Do so with peace of mind with a mechanical camera privacy shutter.

    Bright and beautiful

    Enjoy the rich detail of each pixel with 16:10 FHD+ (1920 x 1200) resolution.

    As a VESA Certified DisplayHDR 500 True Black product, youll uncover new detail in movies and other visuals with astoundingly deep blacks and an extraordinary range of shades.

    VESA Certified DisplayHDR 500 True Black

    A world of versatility

    ersatility is everything with a 360 hinge that is 17% thinner. Edge-to-edge glass-like mylar material across the palmrest and a 30% larger touchpad feels comfortable and luxurious and is resistant to fingerprints and smudges.

    Get going instantly with a lid-open sensor that starts the laptop simply by opening it up, even if completely off or hibernating. Fingerprint reader will verify identity quickly for login using Windows Hello.

    An active pen offers you a natural and accurate writing experience with no pairing required.

    A sleek 65W Type-C power adapter comes with your device. Upgrade to a 90W Type-C power adapter for ExpressCharge capability. ExpressCharge powers your device up to 80% in an hour, so you aren't tethered an outlet.

    Exceptional performance

    This Intel Evo platform brings the perfect combination of performance, responsiveness, battery life and stunning visuals to a new class of sleek, stylish laptops. Co-engineered with Intel and verified to provide the ultimate experience for life or work anywhere.

    Available on select configurations.

    Ports and Slots

    1. SD card reader 2. USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type-A 3. Audio jack

    4. HDMI 1.4 5. USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type-A 6. Thunderbolt 4 (USB Type-C) with Power Delivery and DisplayPort 7. Thunderbolt 4 (USB Type-C) with Power Delivery and DisplayPort
